Commentary Text: Arshdeep Singh to Livingstone, out Caught by Fabian Allen!! This pressure from a quality international batter is good for young Arshdeep Singh. Gives him a bit of send off. And if it's Fabien Allen, as a fielding team you can be very confident. They are checking if the catch is clean, there was never a doubt about it. Arshdeep Singh banged the slower delivery into the wicket and made Livingstone fetch from wide of off stump, Livingstone did pull decently well. The ball was flying to the right of Allen at deep mid-wicket, but he puts in a full length dive and even got both hands to it. Got smashed for a couple of hits, but Arshdeep Singh has come back like he usually does. Livingstone c Fabian Allen b Arshdeep Singh 25(17) [4s-2 6s-1]
